        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(k) He shows that they did not fast with a sincere heart, but because of hypocrisy, and that it was not done from a pure religion, because they lacked these offices of charity which should have declared that they were godly; Mt 23:23.",
        "children": []
      }
