        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " the attitude of the people towards these admonitions of God is described. Nâthan kâthēph sōrereth: to give or offer a rebellious shoulder, as in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
